HEADWORD: Ream
<hw>Ream</hw> <pr>(r⟦emac⟧m)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[AS.
<ets>re⟦aacute⟧m</ets>, akin to G. <ets>rahm</ets>.]</ety> <def>Cream;
